Julius Frankenburg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julius_Frankenburg 0 Julius Frankenberg was an American silent film actor and director. He starred in films such as The Haunted House, Personal Magnetism and A Blowout at Santa Banana working with actors such as Harry von Meter and Louise Lovely. He also directed two silent films.
